      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>ACKERMAN-Sarah, 81, of Coconut Creek, FL. Died June 21, 2000. Beloved wife of the late Aaron Ackerman. Adored mother of Beverly Allen, Marilyn Suzan and Larry Ackerman. Cherished grandmother of six and great grandmother of 3. Dearest friend to devoted, long-term caregiver, Charmaine Glegg and her family. Memorial service to follow.</p>
      </block>
